1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:06,000
The fox demon was gone — but she did not leave.

2
00:00:06,000 --> 00:00:12,000
She lifted her cup, scanning every corner of the garden.

3
00:00:12,000 --> 00:00:17,000
The fox demon was gone — but something else was watching.

4
00:00:17,000 --> 00:00:21,000
— Come out.

5
00:00:21,000 --> 00:00:28,000
A black silhouette emerged from behind the broken rockery.

6
00:00:28,000 --> 00:00:32,000
Who are you?

7
00:00:32,000 --> 00:00:38,000
He said nothing — he only lifted the fox demon's empty cup and breathed in.

8
00:00:38,000 --> 00:00:44,000
Hu Sanlang — owes me a life.

9
00:00:44,000 --> 00:00:49,000
You hold a grudge against him?

10
00:00:49,000 --> 00:00:55,000
No. What he owes — will be repaid in time. But tonight — I came for you.

11
00:00:55,000 --> 00:01:02,000
He lifted his head — a pair of dull grey-white eyes, like two clouded glass orbs.

12
00:01:02,000 --> 00:01:10,000
Lady Lin — the blood of the Demon Ancestor flows in you. The word has spread.

13
00:01:10,000 --> 00:01:17,000
Not only the demons of this palace — but those beyond, now know.

14
00:01:17,000 --> 00:01:23,000
Who spread it?

15
00:01:23,000 --> 00:01:31,000
Before he died — the Snake Demon told his kind. The demon kings of the southern range — know.

16
00:01:31,000 --> 00:01:38,000
They are deliberating — whether to come eat you. Or come crown you.

17
00:01:38,000 --> 00:01:43,000
Crown me?

18
00:01:43,000 --> 00:01:51,000
Crown you as their king. The Demon-Emperor's bloodline — gives you the right.

19
00:01:51,000 --> 00:01:58,000
But most want to eat you — and ascend.

20
00:01:58,000 --> 00:02:05,000
The Demon Ancestor's blood — is a double-edged blade. Power. And countless eyes upon me.

21
00:02:05,000 --> 00:02:10,000
Why tell me this?

22
00:02:10,000 --> 00:02:16,000
Because I too am a demon. I do not wish to be devoured.

23
00:02:16,000 --> 00:02:23,000
If you become the strongest — I will follow you.

24
00:02:23,000 --> 00:02:28,000
You are blunt.

25
00:02:28,000 --> 00:02:33,000
Demons do not lie.

26
00:02:33,000 --> 00:02:41,000
Remember — your time runs short. Three months at most — and they arrive.

27
00:02:41,000 --> 00:02:48,000
He spoke. He vanished into the dark.

28
00:02:48,000 --> 00:02:55,000
Three months — to grow strong enough to face the kings of the southern range.

29
00:02:55,000 --> 00:03:01,000
Or — become someone else's prey.

30
00:03:01,000 --> 00:03:07,000
Looks like — I'll need to speed things up.

31
00:03:07,000 --> 00:03:14,000
Emperor within. Seal below. Ten thousand mountains' kings beyond.

32
00:03:14,000 --> 00:03:20,000
One goal remains: Gold Rank — by the fastest road.
